{"tid":751570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解而家咁多人二十中就結婚？","createTime":"2018-07-22T04:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:45:39.000Z","uid":63913,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"76bc6076e992bf2020b873377dd19897c2fe0139","tid":751570,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"身邊好多人二十中就結婚，就係唔明點解可以咁早。<br />\n<br />\n首先，而家學歷通漲。好多人要讀完master先出黎工作，又有部分人經副學士等路徑先入大學。變相好多人23-24先出黎工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港樓價咁高，班友仔有咩可能做兩三年野就有首期。<br />\n<br />\n最後，周街都玩家同食家，好多人玩左幾年，到三十歲都仲單身。"},{"pid":"845624db1592a3ba76dadb3fad75bcfc09930fd6","tid":751570,"uid":24938,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"因為佢地唔中你講個三個point"},{"pid":"e76a73f3dd1c4ab9824e0a715f8849db27aa531e","tid":751570,"uid":84128,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人地有daddy?"},{"pid":"de00f23160417e560362cb8b5075245c2bc2c871","tid":751570,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"屌你，有女都咁難，仲要有埋樓"},{"pid":"fe3e8579547894679cfaa0d74ca5f98a4d8e3fc1","tid":751570,"uid":82033,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"大陸人普遍早婚<br />\n25已經叫遲"},{"pid":"fdc8ba088df6fa06569e9e602b15ee6bd96a494e","tid":751570,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88b56ec0544cb9041911dbc57687bdf690fee38","tid":751570,"uid":2615,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"唔小心有咗咪要結婚"},{"pid":"b59c7f9ee0cd4d4d126f905a5cc8a48bf0dfb5d9","tid":751570,"uid":121053,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"因為想過多d二人世界 <br />\n仔又唔可以太遲生 想32歲前生<br />\n唔想一結婚就生仔 冇哂生活"},{"pid":"7af07115a1039a4b547744579cd50051c89a8741","tid":751570,"uid":43146,"li